    {
        "text": ">> You're not going to want to miss this episode of the AI Show.",
        "start": 0.0,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "We're going to learn all about",
        "start": 2.55,
        "duration": 1.17
    },
    {
        "text": "the Translator API and cognitive services.",
        "start": 3.72,
        "duration": 2.205
    },
    {
        "text": "It's pretty amazing.",
        "start": 5.925,
        "duration": 1.395
    },
    {
        "text": "Make sure you tune in.",
        "start": 7.32,
        "duration": 0.87
    },
    {
        "text": "[MUSIC]",
        "start": 8.19,
        "duration": 8.31
    },
    {
        "text": "Hello and welcome to this episode of the AI Show,",
        "start": 16.5,
        "duration": 2.295
    },
    {
        "text": "where we're going to talk about",
        "start": 18.795,
        "duration": 1.035
    },
    {
        "text": "Translator API and cognitive services.",
        "start": 19.83,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "I got a special guest, my friend.",
        "start": 21.72,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "Hello. Tell us who you are and what you do.",
        "start": 23.4,
        "duration": 2.31
    },
    {
        "text": ">> Hey, Seth. Hello, nice talking with you.",
        "start": 25.71,
        "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
        "text": "My name is Chris Wendt",
        "start": 27.99,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "and I'm the Group Program Manager",
        "start": 29.01,
        "duration": 1.41
    },
    {
        "text": "for Microsoft Translation Service.",
        "start": 30.42,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": ">> All right. So let's dive in.",
        "start": 32.16,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "What is the translation service?",
        "start": 33.6,
        "duration": 2.31
    },
    {
        "text": "Why is it important?",
        "start": 35.91,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "How to use it. Let's get into it.",
        "start": 36.93,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": ">> All right. I'd love to talk about it.",
        "start": 38.7,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "The translation service translates.",
        "start": 42.14,
        "duration": 2.205
    },
    {
        "text": "It translates between natural language",
        "start": 44.345,
        "duration": 2.505
    },
    {
        "text": "and it translates speech,",
        "start": 46.85,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "and it translates text.",
        "start": 49.01,
        "duration": 1.635
    },
    {
        "text": "Text is really a pretty simple thing.",
        "start": 50.645,
        "duration": 2.565
    },
    {
        "text": "You give it a piece of text,",
        "start": 53.21,
        "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
        "text": "it returns to you the translation of that piece of text.",
        "start": 54.29,
        "duration": 4.005
    },
    {
        "text": "Speech is a little more complicated",
        "start": 58.295,
        "duration": 1.785
    },
    {
        "text": "and I want to introduce you to both today.",
        "start": 60.08,
        "duration": 2.475
    },
    {
        "text": "We are, of course, motivated",
        "start": 62.555,
        "duration": 1.845
    },
    {
        "text": "by breaking down the language barrier between people.",
        "start": 64.4,
        "duration": 2.91
    },
    {
        "text": "We want people to communicate,",
        "start": 67.31,
        "duration": 2.115
    },
    {
        "text": "people to talk to each other.",
        "start": 69.425,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "In fact, not just people talking to each other,",
        "start": 71.645,
        "duration": 2.615
    },
    {
        "text": "it's also machines interpreting",
        "start": 74.26,
        "duration": 4.12
    },
    {
        "text": "what people are writing",
        "start": 78.38,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "in order for processing it or just to render it",
        "start": 80.81,
        "duration": 5.41
    },
    {
        "text": "for another human or for some AI that you want to run on it.",
        "start": 86.22,
        "duration": 5.49
    },
    {
        "text": "Say, for instance, to extract information",
        "start": 91.71,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "out of a translated document.",
        "start": 94.04,
        "duration": 1.635
    },
    {
        "text": "So breaking down language barriers is what we do,",
        "start": 95.675,
        "duration": 3.075
    },
    {
        "text": "that's in our DNA.",
        "start": 98.75,
        "duration": 2.835
    },
    {
        "text": "What's important for you to know is",
        "start": 101.585,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "that automating translation is really cheap.",
        "start": 104.465,
        "duration": 4.78
    },
    {
        "text": "It's about in fact 1,000 cheaper than human translations.",
        "start": 109.245,
        "duration": 5.435
    },
    {
        "text": "So you can do a lot more with it.",
        "start": 114.68,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "It is infinitely faster.",
        "start": 117.2,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "It is however, not as good.",
        "start": 119.3,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "You don't get as good a translation out of it.",
        "start": 121.12,
        "duration": 4.79
    },
    {
        "text": "There's a difference between languages.",
        "start": 125.91,
        "duration": 4.38
    },
    {
        "text": "So the most translated languages of the world generally,",
        "start": 130.29,
        "duration": 2.97
    },
    {
        "text": "I say the 20 most translated languages",
        "start": 133.26,
        "duration": 4.095
    },
    {
        "text": "of the world that includes French, German, Italian,",
        "start": 137.355,
        "duration": 2.585
    },
    {
        "text": "and Spanish, Chinese, Japanese,",
        "start": 139.94,
        "duration": 2.325
    },
    {
        "text": "Portuguese, and a bunch more.",
        "start": 142.265,
        "duration": 3.47
    },
    {
        "text": "They translate really well.",
        "start": 145.735,
        "duration": 2.205
    },
    {
        "text": "As you move out of those most translated languages,",
        "start": 147.94,
        "duration": 4.63
    },
    {
        "text": "there's just less training material available.",
        "start": 152.57,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "So the vocabulary coverage and the fluency",
        "start": 155.18,
        "duration": 4.2
    },
    {
        "text": "just goes down a little bit",
        "start": 159.38,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "for the languages that are not in the top 10.",
        "start": 161.81,
        "duration": 3.255
    },
    {
        "text": "So here I have calculated what it costs.",
        "start": 165.065,
        "duration": 5.835
    },
    {
        "text": "To translate a million words,",
        "start": 170.9,
        "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
        "text": "you pay about $250,000 to have",
        "start": 174.32,
        "duration": 3.57
    },
    {
        "text": "that translated in human translation quality with the machine.",
        "start": 177.89,
        "duration": 3.705
    },
    {
        "text": "That's our most expensive service.",
        "start": 181.595,
        "duration": 4.125
    },
    {
        "text": "That's the customized machine translation and functionality",
        "start": 185.72,
        "duration": 4.335
    },
    {
        "text": "that costs you $280 to translate the same amount.",
        "start": 190.055,
        "duration": 6.0
    },
    {
        "text": ">> That's for the most expensive one too?",
        "start": 196.055,
        "duration": 2.15
    },
    {
        "text": ">> That's the most expensive.",
        "start": 198.205,
        "duration": 1.495
    },
    {
        "text": "The cheapest one would cost you $70.",
        "start": 199.7,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": ">> Holy cow.",
        "start": 202.46,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": ">> Yeah. That is quite a difference.",
        "start": 204.25,
        "duration": 3.265
    },
    {
        "text": "So you get a much cheaper price.",
        "start": 207.515,
        "duration": 3.495
    },
    {
        "text": "You get infinitely faster.",
        "start": 211.01,
        "duration": 1.785
    },
    {
        "text": "But you pay for it in quality.",
        "start": 212.795,
        "duration": 3.87
    },
    {
        "text": "But how bad really is the quality?",
        "start": 216.665,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "So a quick history.",
        "start": 219.305,
        "duration": 1.83
    },
    {
        "text": "Machine translation is old.",
        "start": 221.135,
        "duration": 2.085
    },
    {
        "text": "It was invented in the 1950s,",
        "start": 223.22,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "and it has made steady advances since then.",
        "start": 226.18,
        "duration": 4.015
    },
    {
        "text": "So every 5 to 10 years you have",
        "start": 230.195,
        "duration": 2.415
    },
    {
        "text": "a major algorithmic improvement.",
        "start": 232.61,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "The latest one was really the neural networks,",
        "start": 235.73,
        "duration": 4.12
    },
    {
        "text": "and specifically the transformer models",
        "start": 239.85,
        "duration": 1.985
    },
    {
        "text": "inside the neural networks have",
        "start": 241.835,
        "duration": 2.805
    },
    {
        "text": "brought us the latest noticeable increase in quality.",
        "start": 244.64,
        "duration": 5.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Between these 5 to 10 years,",
        "start": 249.8,
        "duration": 3.53
    },
    {
        "text": "we can improve the automatic translation quality by",
        "start": 253.33,
        "duration": 6.595
    },
    {
        "text": "adding new or better filtered training material",
        "start": 259.925,
        "duration": 4.565
    },
    {
        "text": "and you can do the same.",
        "start": 264.49,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "You can adjust or improve the translation quality",
        "start": 266.41,
        "duration": 4.36
    },
    {
        "text": "for your terminology and domain",
        "start": 270.77,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "by using a feature that we have,",
        "start": 273.53,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "it's called Custom Translator that allows you",
        "start": 275.78,
        "duration": 3.18
    },
    {
        "text": "to upload previously translated documents.",
        "start": 278.96,
        "duration": 3.39
    },
    {
        "text": "You don't need that many of them,",
        "start": 282.35,
        "duration": 2.93
    },
    {
        "text": "about 10,000 sentences is the minimum,",
        "start": 285.28,
        "duration": 3.64
    },
    {
        "text": "20,000 will create a noticeable difference.",
        "start": 288.92,
        "duration": 4.755
    },
    {
        "text": "Anything above that is,",
        "start": 293.675,
        "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
        "text": "helpful as its goodness.",
        "start": 295.695,
        "duration": 2.485
    },
    {
        "text": "Then you build a system that knows",
        "start": 298.18,
        "duration": 3.01
    },
    {
        "text": "your terminology and style much better than our generic system.",
        "start": 301.19,
        "duration": 3.33
    },
    {
        "text": ">> This is really cool because most people don't know this.",
        "start": 304.52,
        "duration": 3.21
    },
    {
        "text": "Maybe you know this, but I basically",
        "start": 307.73,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "did research in machine translation.",
        "start": 310.16,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "That's what I went to school for.",
        "start": 312.26,
        "duration": 1.29
    },
    {
        "text": "I studied the IBM models 1 through 5.",
        "start": 313.55,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "I went to school right before",
        "start": 316.31,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "neural networks became popular again,",
        "start": 317.84,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "hence, it's really cool to see this history.",
        "start": 319.85,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "It's really cool to see a semi-supervised approach too",
        "start": 322.31,
        "duration": 3.51
    },
    {
        "text": "where you give it some information",
        "start": 325.82,
        "duration": 2.099
    },
    {
        "text": "and it gets a little bit better from there.",
        "start": 327.919,
        "duration": 1.806
    },
    {
        "text": ">> Yes, exactly.",
        "start": 329.725,
        "duration": 2.435
    },
    {
        "text": "So the goal is to reach human parity.",
        "start": 332.16,
        "duration": 4.935
    },
    {
        "text": "Be as good as a human.",
        "start": 337.095,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "In 2018, we said we have reached it in",
        "start": 340.455,
        "duration": 3.665
    },
    {
        "text": "the Chinese to English news domain,",
        "start": 344.12,
        "duration": 3.315
    },
    {
        "text": "by just comparing it to human translator and then have",
        "start": 347.435,
        "duration": 2.985
    },
    {
        "text": "a judge go judge it sentence by sentence.",
        "start": 350.42,
        "duration": 4.31
    },
    {
        "text": "So in that newest domain it worked okay because",
        "start": 354.73,
        "duration": 3.22
    },
    {
        "text": "fairly clean language that is published in news.",
        "start": 357.95,
        "duration": 4.275
    },
    {
        "text": "Where you translate more difficult stuff",
        "start": 362.225,
        "duration": 2.415
    },
    {
        "text": "like what we are talking out,",
        "start": 364.64,
        "duration": 2.37
    },
    {
        "text": "it's not perfectly clean or when you have chat messages also,",
        "start": 367.01,
        "duration": 3.57
    },
    {
        "text": "it's not perfectly clean as it's not necessarily",
        "start": 370.58,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "grammatically correct with the right casing and punctuation.",
        "start": 373.94,
        "duration": 3.75
    },
    {
        "text": "It falls off, the human still does better.",
        "start": 377.69,
        "duration": 5.18
    },
    {
        "text": "So I want to talk now a little bit about",
        "start": 382.87,
        "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
        "text": "how you actually use it in your application.",
        "start": 386.03,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "So translation of text is a very simple process.",
        "start": 388.46,
        "duration": 5.49
    },
    {
        "text": "So it has one function that's called Translate.",
        "start": 393.95,
        "duration": 2.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Sorry, that's not one function.",
        "start": 396.73,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "Still the most important function above everything else.",
        "start": 398.55,
        "duration": 4.635
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a stateless REST API.",
        "start": 403.185,
        "duration": 2.914
    },
    {
        "text": "You give it a piece of text, in adjacent package,",
        "start": 406.099,
        "duration": 3.971
    },
    {
        "text": "you get back that same text in",
        "start": 410.07,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "the other language in adjacent package. That's pretty much it.",
        "start": 412.55,
        "duration": 3.555
    },
    {
        "text": "The input formats are plain text or HTML.",
        "start": 416.105,
        "duration": 3.675
    },
    {
        "text": "You can translate between 1 and 70 languages, any to any.",
        "start": 419.78,
        "duration": 6.39
    },
    {
        "text": "You don't have to specify the source language.",
        "start": 426.17,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "You can just let the system guess what the source language was.",
        "start": 428.84,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "But you need to specify one or more target languages.",
        "start": 431.57,
        "duration": 3.69
    },
    {
        "text": "You can translate to multiple languages",
        "start": 435.26,
        "duration": 2.159
    },
    {
        "text": "at once in the same request.",
        "start": 437.419,
        "duration": 3.105
    },
    {
        "text": "Then you get just different rows in your JSON array.",
        "start": 440.524,
        "duration": 7.096
    },
    {
        "text": ">> So you don't have to tell it the input language,",
        "start": 447.62,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "you just tell it the output languages.",
        "start": 450.5,
        "duration": 1.91
    },
    {
        "text": ">> Yeah, you have the option to tell it.",
        "start": 452.41,
        "duration": 1.85
    },
    {
        "text": "If you are sure what it is,",
        "start": 454.26,
        "duration": 3.83
    },
    {
        "text": "then you can specify it.",
        "start": 458.09,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "So there are no detection mistake.",
        "start": 459.74,
        "duration": 1.785
    },
    {
        "text": "The text detection works quite safely.",
        "start": 461.525,
        "duration": 3.715
    },
    {
        "text": "It's unlikely to make",
        "start": 465.24,
        "duration": 4.04
    },
    {
        "text": "mistakes except for very closely related languages.",
        "start": 469.28,
        "duration": 3.45
    },
    {
        "text": "So for instance, between Russia and Ukraine",
        "start": 472.73,
        "duration": 2.37
    },
    {
        "text": "and it may pick one or the other.",
        "start": 475.1,
        "duration": 2.265
    },
    {
        "text": "Because they have very similar character sequences in them.",
        "start": 477.365,
        "duration": 7.665
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, and that's how it works or Danish and Swedish,",
        "start": 485.03,
        "duration": 2.715
    },
    {
        "text": "they are also somewhat confusable.",
        "start": 487.745,
        "duration": 1.874
    },
    {
        "text": "But generally, it works very safely",
        "start": 489.619,
        "duration": 4.561
    },
    {
        "text": "even for short push word strengths.",
        "start": 494.18,
        "duration": 3.265
    },
    {
        "text": "The next function here on this list is the Languages function.",
        "start": 497.445,
        "duration": 3.785
    },
    {
        "text": "It's just an enumeration tells you",
        "start": 501.23,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "which languages you can translate between.",
        "start": 503.15,
        "duration": 2.09
    },
    {
        "text": "It also gives you the friendly name of the language so you can",
        "start": 505.24,
        "duration": 3.07
    },
    {
        "text": "render it in your UI",
        "start": 508.31,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "to have the user choose in whatever language we translate.",
        "start": 509.93,
        "duration": 3.78
    },
    {
        "text": "We also give you the language name",
        "start": 513.71,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "so that you can allow a user to choose from it.",
        "start": 515.36,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Plus all the other things you can do with a particular language.",
        "start": 518.12,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "So not all languages, for instance,",
        "start": 520.88,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "have a transliteration, which is the next function here.",
        "start": 522.65,
        "duration": 3.045
    },
    {
        "text": "So Transliteration is to change the script of a piece of text,",
        "start": 525.695,
        "duration": 7.395
    },
    {
        "text": "say between a native script and the romanized script.",
        "start": 533.09,
        "duration": 3.45
    },
    {
        "text": "For instance, if you have Arabic or Chinese,",
        "start": 536.54,
        "duration": 2.909
    },
    {
        "text": "there's a Latin script version of it",
        "start": 539.449,
        "duration": 4.351
    },
    {
        "text": "that makes it readable for people who",
        "start": 543.8,
        "duration": 3.58
    },
    {
        "text": "don't read the characters of the language,",
        "start": 547.38,
        "duration": 4.43
    },
    {
        "text": "but still want to understand it or learn it also.",
        "start": 551.81,
        "duration": 2.655
    },
    {
        "text": "So it's really good for language learning scenarios.",
        "start": 554.465,
        "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Detection just tells you what the language was of a piece of text,",
        "start": 558.365,
        "duration": 4.2
    },
    {
        "text": "just in case you want to base",
        "start": 562.565,
        "duration": 2.175
    },
    {
        "text": "your further processing on it",
        "start": 564.74,
        "duration": 1.995
    },
    {
        "text": "without invoking the translation function.",
        "start": 566.735,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "Then BreakSentences tells you",
        "start": 569.195,
        "duration": 1.785
    },
    {
        "text": "the boundaries of sentences in your text.",
        "start": 570.98,
        "duration": 5.69
    },
    {
        "text": "This is important when you want to translate",
        "start": 576.67,
        "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
        "text": "a long stretch of text,",
        "start": 579.25,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "say, a longer document,",
        "start": 582.31,
        "duration": 1.71
    },
    {
        "text": "longer than the request size limit,",
        "start": 584.02,
        "duration": 2.79
    },
    {
        "text": "which is 5,000 characters.",
        "start": 586.81,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "So then you need to find the last sentence break",
        "start": 588.37,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "because you cannot translate partial sentences.",
        "start": 590.5,
        "duration": 2.385
    },
    {
        "text": "You can translate them, but it'll produce a bad translation.",
        "start": 592.885,
        "duration": 3.555
    },
    {
        "text": ">> Got it.",
        "start": 596.44,
        "duration": 0.21
    },
    {
        "text": ">> So you always need to keep sentences intact,",
        "start": 596.65,
        "duration": 1.905
    },
    {
        "text": "and the break sentence method helps you with it.",
        "start": 598.555,
        "duration": 3.135
    },
    {
        "text": "That's already it, Seth.",
        "start": 601.69,
        "duration": 2.985
    },
    {
        "text": "There's not much more to it.",
        "start": 604.675,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "Very simple API, very simple functionality.",
        "start": 607.345,
        "duration": 6.285
    },
    {
        "text": "I want to mention, as I talked a lot about",
        "start": 613.63,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "the translating longer documents or longer strings,",
        "start": 616.69,
        "duration": 3.81
    },
    {
        "text": "we have some sample code on",
        "start": 620.5,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "our GitHub repo that helps you do that.",
        "start": 622.3,
        "duration": 2.97
    },
    {
        "text": "We're also working on a document translation API",
        "start": 625.27,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "where you can submit a whole document intact",
        "start": 627.94,
        "duration": 3.27
    },
    {
        "text": "and you don't have to break it by hand.",
        "start": 631.21,
        "duration": 3.285
    },
    {
        "text": "I think that'll be useful.",
        "start": 634.495,
        "duration": 2.085
    },
    {
        "text": ">> This is impressive because you say that's it.",
        "start": 636.58,
        "duration": 2.385
    },
    {
        "text": "It's just basically a function to translate a language.",
        "start": 638.965,
        "duration": 2.91
    },
    {
        "text": "Like I said, I'd worked on noisy channel models from",
        "start": 641.875,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "the IBM series of things in",
        "start": 644.935,
        "duration": 2.325
    },
    {
        "text": "the '90s that I was doing research with in the late 2000s.",
        "start": 647.26,
        "duration": 3.75
    },
    {
        "text": "So this is just not just a function,",
        "start": 651.01,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "this is pure AI magic.",
        "start": 653.89,
        "duration": 2.07
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you have some code you can show us?",
        "start": 655.96,
        "duration": 2.025
    },
    {
        "text": ">> Yes. I want to move on to speech,",
        "start": 657.985,
        "duration": 3.66
    },
    {
        "text": "which is actually a little more",
        "start": 661.645,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": "magical than the translation of text.",
        "start": 663.385,
        "duration": 5.475
    },
    {
        "text": "It's more magical because it really combines",
        "start": 668.86,
        "duration": 3.69
    },
    {
        "text": "two very interesting services,",
        "start": 672.55,
        "duration": 4.305
    },
    {
        "text": "the speech recognition and the translation.",
        "start": 676.855,
        "duration": 3.255
    },
    {
        "text": "There's a lot of",
        "start": 680.11,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "shared technology below the surface because they do similar thing.",
        "start": 681.13,
        "duration": 8.325
    },
    {
        "text": "They take in a stream of, let's say,",
        "start": 689.455,
        "duration": 6.03
    },
    {
        "text": "audio or a stream of",
        "start": 695.485,
        "duration": 2.535
    },
    {
        "text": "text and then give you a return to use some markup,",
        "start": 698.02,
        "duration": 3.375
    },
    {
        "text": "either the translation or the text of the recognition.",
        "start": 701.395,
        "duration": 5.61
    },
    {
        "text": "They are both not 100 percent reliable.",
        "start": 707.005,
        "duration": 3.165
    },
    {
        "text": "They both make mistakes.",
        "start": 710.17,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "So if you combine these two,",
        "start": 711.19,
        "duration": 1.71
    },
    {
        "text": "you have a chance to multiply the mistakes.",
        "start": 712.9,
        "duration": 6.07
    },
    {
        "text": "Pretty much the world, it took us a while to be",
        "start": 719.88,
        "duration": 2.71
    },
    {
        "text": "brave enough to put these two together.",
        "start": 722.59,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "But now both technologies,",
        "start": 724.6,
        "duration": 1.619
    },
    {
        "text": "the speech recognition and the translation have",
        "start": 726.219,
        "duration": 3.661
    },
    {
        "text": "reached a level where you can really do that, combine those two.",
        "start": 729.88,
        "duration": 4.32
    },
    {
        "text": "So I have listed here the steps of what's necessary in order",
        "start": 734.2,
        "duration": 6.075
    },
    {
        "text": "to embark on the translating speech.",
        "start": 740.275,
        "duration": 7.65
    },
    {
        "text": "For this, we offer a nice client side SDK.",
        "start": 747.925,
        "duration": 5.025
    },
    {
        "text": "For a translation of text,",
        "start": 752.95,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "you don't really need that. It's so simple.",
        "start": 754.54,
        "duration": 3.09
    },
    {
        "text": "But for speech is processed using",
        "start": 757.63,
        "duration": 4.83
    },
    {
        "text": "a streaming protocol and that's fairly hard to manage by hand.",
        "start": 762.46,
        "duration": 5.79
    },
    {
        "text": "So we give you an SDK that's",
        "start": 768.25,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "available for all the major operating system and",
        "start": 770.35,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "all the major programming languages",
        "start": 772.69,
        "duration": 3.195
    },
    {
        "text": "so it's meant to fit your need.",
        "start": 775.885,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "So let me just go to the example here.",
        "start": 779.425,
        "duration": 3.555
    },
    {
        "text": "This is the simplest example that you can come up with.",
        "start": 782.98,
        "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
        "text": "This is the whole thing.",
        "start": 786.4,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Let me zoom in a little bit so that you can see it in pieces.",
        "start": 787.9,
        "duration": 6.345
    },
    {
        "text": "You see here at the top,",
        "start": 794.245,
        "duration": 2.085
    },
    {
        "text": "you just include the speech SDK,",
        "start": 796.33,
        "duration": 4.23
    },
    {
        "text": "then you state what your source and your target language is.",
        "start": 800.56,
        "duration": 3.765
    },
    {
        "text": "Speech also allows you to do language detection.",
        "start": 804.325,
        "duration": 5.58
    },
    {
        "text": "It can detect only between a small set of languages.",
        "start": 809.905,
        "duration": 3.705
    },
    {
        "text": "Detection of the speech language",
        "start": 813.61,
        "duration": 4.05
    },
    {
        "text": "is much harder than the detection of a text language.",
        "start": 817.66,
        "duration": 3.675
    },
    {
        "text": "So in this example here,",
        "start": 821.335,
        "duration": 2.025
    },
    {
        "text": "we specify it because either I speak only two languages,",
        "start": 823.36,
        "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
        "text": "so it's not really that hard.",
        "start": 826.78,
        "duration": 2.355
    },
    {
        "text": "I can say I can speak either English or German and that's it,",
        "start": 829.135,
        "duration": 4.14
    },
    {
        "text": "and here I chose to translate it to German.",
        "start": 833.275,
        "duration": 2.49
    },
    {
        "text": "Then you simply wait for the recognizer to give you a result,",
        "start": 835.765,
        "duration": 6.21
    },
    {
        "text": "and then you do something with it.",
        "start": 841.975,
        "duration": 4.2
    },
    {
        "text": "If there's success, in this case,",
        "start": 846.175,
        "duration": 3.855
    },
    {
        "text": "this API just prints out the recognition and the translation.",
        "start": 850.03,
        "duration": 7.5
    },
    {
        "text": "What this doesn't show is that you",
        "start": 857.53,
        "duration": 3.165
    },
    {
        "text": "get the partial results while I'm talking.",
        "start": 860.695,
        "duration": 4.215
    },
    {
        "text": "So you can do real-time actions before the end of the utterance.",
        "start": 864.91,
        "duration": 5.28
    },
    {
        "text": "Then I have an example here,",
        "start": 870.19,
        "duration": 2.205
    },
    {
        "text": "if I may show that.",
        "start": 872.395,
        "duration": 1.83
    },
    {
        "text": "That's okay, that's great that I can show that.",
        "start": 874.225,
        "duration": 3.57
    },
    {
        "text": "That is on GitHub in the Azure speech",
        "start": 877.795,
        "duration": 7.125
    },
    {
        "text": "SDK repo that shows how it all works nicely together.",
        "start": 884.92,
        "duration": 7.56
    },
    {
        "text": "So it's a fairly ugly UI as it's supposed to be for a demo app.",
        "start": 892.48,
        "duration": 7.725
    },
    {
        "text": "I choose here which language I'm speaking,",
        "start": 900.205,
        "duration": 3.33
    },
    {
        "text": "so I'm speaking English here.",
        "start": 903.535,
        "duration": 1.83
    },
    {
        "text": "I want to translate it to Chinese and to German.",
        "start": 905.365,
        "duration": 2.385
    },
    {
        "text": "Just the same thing here.",
        "start": 907.75,
        "duration": 0.93
    },
    {
        "text": "You can translate to multiple languages at once.",
        "start": 908.68,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "As part of the API,",
        "start": 911.2,
        "duration": 2.055
    },
    {
        "text": "you get for free,",
        "start": 913.255,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "the audio of one of these languages.",
        "start": 914.755,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "So I can choose that here as well.",
        "start": 917.815,
        "duration": 2.805
    },
    {
        "text": "We wanted to do that way to enable, say,",
        "start": 920.62,
        "duration": 3.585
    },
    {
        "text": "real-time conversations between people.",
        "start": 924.205,
        "duration": 3.735
    },
    {
        "text": "So that I can speak something and then my app",
        "start": 927.94,
        "duration": 4.26
    },
    {
        "text": "can make myself be heard in the other language.",
        "start": 932.2,
        "duration": 5.325
    },
    {
        "text": "This way you can build a bidirectional conversation.",
        "start": 937.525,
        "duration": 5.055
    },
    {
        "text": "Let me show you how that works.",
        "start": 942.58,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Hello, how are you doing today?\"",
        "start": 946.11,
        "duration": 3.41
    },
    {
        "text": "If you listen carefully,",
        "start": 954.99,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "you heard the Chinese is coming out of my system speaker here.",
        "start": 957.55,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "So let's do it again.",
        "start": 960.91,
        "duration": 4.185
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, I'm saying something that's a little longer so that you",
        "start": 965.095,
        "duration": 3.765
    },
    {
        "text": "can see the partial results as I'm speaking.",
        "start": 968.86,
        "duration": 4.75
    },
    {
        "text": "You can see the results of my recognition as I am speaking.",
        "start": 974.28,
        "duration": 4.6
    },
    {
        "text": "[FOREIGN]",
        "start": 978.88,
        "duration": 6.09
    },
    {
        "text": "So you not only get the final after I'm done,",
        "start": 984.97,
        "duration": 3.57
    },
    {
        "text": "but you also get the interim",
        "start": 988.54,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "in all the languages that are involved here,",
        "start": 990.13,
        "duration": 3.39
    },
    {
        "text": "which is the original and two",
        "start": 993.52,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "translations and one of them as all of them.",
        "start": 995.05,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": ">> That's really cool. I also heard",
        "start": 997.03,
        "duration": 2.055
    },
    {
        "text": "the Chinese through your system audio. That was really cool.",
        "start": 999.085,
        "duration": 4.89
    },
    {
        "text": ">> Yeah, good.",
        "start": 1003.975,
        "duration": 2.925
    },
    {
        "text": "So let me go to the next one here.",
        "start": 1006.9,
        "duration": 4.035
    },
    {
        "text": "You asked what are the other cool things that are coming up.",
        "start": 1010.935,
        "duration": 5.745
    },
    {
        "text": "So imagine it's not just the two of us talking to each other",
        "start": 1016.68,
        "duration": 5.925
    },
    {
        "text": "but there is a whole group of people and they",
        "start": 1022.605,
        "duration": 3.135
    },
    {
        "text": "all want to listen to each other,",
        "start": 1025.74,
        "duration": 3.09
    },
    {
        "text": "however, they don't share the same language.",
        "start": 1028.83,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "So on our journey to break down the language barriers,",
        "start": 1031.56,
        "duration": 4.47
    },
    {
        "text": "we are building a system",
        "start": 1036.03,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "that really represents a conversation in the Cloud,",
        "start": 1038.7,
        "duration": 3.48
    },
    {
        "text": "and each audio channel feeds into that conversation in the Cloud,",
        "start": 1042.18,
        "duration": 4.26
    },
    {
        "text": "and the Cloud distributes the transcript",
        "start": 1046.44,
        "duration": 2.49
    },
    {
        "text": "and translation to everybody who is participating.",
        "start": 1048.93,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "That's really the idea behind it.",
        "start": 1051.81,
        "duration": 2.805
    },
    {
        "text": "It's also consumable via the speech SDK.",
        "start": 1054.615,
        "duration": 2.655
    },
    {
        "text": "It's currently in private preview",
        "start": 1057.27,
        "duration": 1.71
    },
    {
        "text": "and we'd like to invite you to participate in it",
        "start": 1058.98,
        "duration": 5.025
    },
    {
        "text": "and try it out and let us know",
        "start": 1064.005,
        "duration": 3.015
    },
    {
        "text": "what you would like to see in this functionality.",
        "start": 1067.02,
        "duration": 5.13
    },
    {
        "text": ">> This is all pretty amazing stuff.",
        "start": 1072.15,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "Where can people go to find out more?",
        "start": 1074.7,
        "duration": 2.23
    },
    {
        "text": ">> People can visit us on the web at Microsoft.com/translator.",
        "start": 1078.02,
        "duration": 5.095
    },
    {
        "text": "You see our GitHub repo as well here under Microsoft Translator.",
        "start": 1083.115,
        "duration": 5.16
    },
    {
        "text": "You can submit questions on Stack Overflow,",
        "start": 1088.275,
        "duration": 4.905
    },
    {
        "text": "we monitor that. Or you can tweet us.",
        "start": 1093.18,
        "duration": 3.345
    },
    {
        "text": ">> Well, my friend, this has all been pretty amazing.",
        "start": 1096.525,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you so much for spending some time with us.",
        "start": 1100.365,
        "duration": 2.385
    },
    {
        "text": "For those who are watching, thank you so much for coming.",
        "start": 1102.75,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "You were learning all about what's new",
        "start": 1104.97,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "in Cognitive Services Translator API.",
        "start": 1106.74,
        "duration": 1.965
    },
    {
        "text": "We got a whirlwind tour of some of",
        "start": 1108.705,
        "duration": 1.665
    },
    {
        "text": "the amazing things you can build today.",
        "start": 1110.37,
        "duration": 2.505
    },
    {
        "text": "We'll see you next time. Take care, my friends.",
        "start": 1112.875,
        "duration": 1.635
    },
    {
        "text": "[MUSIC]",
        "start": 1114.51,
        "duration": 14.49
    }
]